This directory contains clock correction files appropriate for the NANOGrav
15-year dataset. Note that PINT uses clock corrections from the global 
pulsar-clock-corrections repository: 

    https://ipta.github.io/pulsar-clock-corrections/

To install these files manually, see PINT documentation:

    https://nanograv-pint.readthedocs.io/en/latest/explanation.html#clock-corrections.
